   <talk_paragraph index="n1579_for_memory-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-2-e" mid="104" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9442_qu_02.ogg}<BR>She's the fragment of Vestinel you've summoned from Mistland! Father, please come back to your senses... I'm sure the Goddess doesn't want to destroy this world. Have you forgotten all our dreams, all the Goddess's dreams?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1579_for_memory-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-2-f" mid="105" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9442_qu_03.ogg}<BR>We never saw such tragedies or the end of Lagendia in our dreams. What we saw was utopia, like the land of the Gods!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1579_for_memory-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-2-g" mid="106" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9442_qu_04.ogg}<BR>It was only after the Goddess drank Vestinel's poison and Ancient Dragon's death that we saw darkness in Her dreams. How can you confidently say taht you are the Goddess's creation when you forget about all that blinded by the poison?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1579_for_memory-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-2-h" mid="107" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Arno${sound:npc_Arno_9442_qu_02.ogg}<BR>My daughter, a dream is nothing but a dream. If the darkness entered Her dreams, it is only natural that we must turn to darkness too. This is nature's law!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1579_for_memory-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="NPC_Left_Arno.dds" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Gaharam.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-2-i" mid="108" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Gaharam${sound:npc_Gaharam_9442_qu_05.ogg}<BR>But we have our own will! We are the ones who remember the Goddess's will! We must help the Goddess if she is in pain. The Goddess must have created us and the dragons for that very reason!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
