      <talk_answer link_index="n1579_for_memory-7" mid="122" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta${sound:npc_Argenta_9442_qu_02.ogg}<BR>He doesn't remember?! Even after being corrupted he shouldn't have gone this far! This... this is... how did you know about this? What kind of experiments were you doing?! What have you done??!!!</html>]]></talk_question>
