   <talk_paragraph index="n1566_pether-8" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Pether.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1566_pether-8-a" mid="127" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Feder? Meriendel?! Why am I here?!! I was with Arno and Argenta a moment ago...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1566_pether-8-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Pether.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1566_pether-8-b" mid="128" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Feder$<BR>Is this the human you brought to see me, Meriendel? <BR>A fool who can't even control himself against the power of the Monolith!<BR>Now why don't you tell this weak being about that truth of yours too?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1566_pether-8-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Pether.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1566_pether-9" mid="129" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Feder...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1566_pether-9" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Pether.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1566_pether-9-" mid="98" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Feder$<BR>It's unlike you to hide the truth on such fear.<BR>I didn't know you were a coward. Now why don't you tell that human, the despair of the truth?!<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Feder disappears)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-a" mid="131" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Are you alright...? Has the Monolith swept you in another time period again?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-b" mid="132" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I think so... Anyway, what happened? Have you told him everything?<BR>About the Ancients, and the seal stone...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-c" mid="133" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>Ah... so that's all you know. Maybe I should have stopped at that when I told Feder the truth. I figured he would be fine even if he found out that this world was built on the screams of the others. I thought he would accept it even if he thought this was not his ideal world...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-d" mid="134" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Meriendel...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-e" mid="135" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_02.ogg}<BR>But the truth has made him tormented in such a despair! No matter how strong his beliefs may be, he still is a human...<BR>Ah... I never expected I would be the one who would break his conviction. This is agonizing...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
