<FONT color=#662500>What else do you know?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-g" mid="137" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>I would like to ask you too. What have you witnessed while you were gone? You have disappeared into the darkness and suddenly appeared like this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-h" mid="138" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_03.ogg}<BR>I can tell that you have seen so many answers and grief during that short time.<BR>What have you seen, and what made you grieved?<BR>I need to know if it is something that happened in the Monolith.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-i" mid="139" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>...I was stuck in the past for some time.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#662500>From the Ancient times till now... </FONT><FONT color=#662500>(Tell her everything you saw)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-j" mid="140" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR>...!!<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meriendel stares at you in suprise)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-k" mid="141" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I thought maybe I could change history, since I already knew the outcome. But I couldn't change a thing! All I could do was get swept along in the action. Gaharam said it was all part of my fate... So my fate is to watch tragedies without being able to do anything...?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-l" mid="143" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>My present world isn't looking good either. I don't know if Argenta is alright, and I'm stuck here in the past... Why did I come to the Monolith? I don't know... I seriously don't know what to do! I...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-m" mid="144" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Meriendel reaches out for your hands and holds them tightly)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-n" mid="145" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Meriendel..?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-o" mid="146" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_04.ogg}<BR>Pala Telesia. Destiny is what leads you, and the things you have seen were shown to you for a reason. Kind soul, please don't be sad that you have failed to change the fate of this world.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-p" mid="147" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_05.ogg}<BR>Though a sad and painful fate it may be, I'm sure it will be the foundation for the future.<BR>Please don't forget what you've seen. Everyone from the corrupted ones, those who tried to save them, people who cared for you, and people who hated you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-q" mid="149" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>$Archer Meriendel${sound:npc_Marriendel_9442_qu_06.ogg}<BR>...and since you have learnt the past, I have realized that I have to tell you about the truth.<BR>I will tell you everything I know, the truth that I told Feder.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Marriendel.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-r" mid="150" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>The truth...?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1571_meriendel-9-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1571_meriendel-9-s" mid="153" select_type="4" />
